text:
I'm not ready to give that up yet
     because meat by itself has a lot of negativity attached to it because
     the slaughtering of the animal, the energy that the animal leaves
     behind, the fact that the animal went through a very gruesome murder
     and the fact that the animal surrounded by a lot of dirtiness, a lot of
     just very horrible things.
name: Cuauhtémoc
